treatment-experienced patients.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/34637/', '', 'Tinidazole, Levofloxacin, Tetracycline, Sucralfate, Misoprostol, Bismuth subcitrate potassium, Amoxicillin', 'Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Lenacapavir, Telaprevir, Etravirine, More', 1767369485);
